reviewText: I don't care what anyone else says, Chop Kick Panda is one of the funnies low-budget cartoons I have ever seen. The jokes are just so clever! Yeah, the animation is sub-par, but it's not hideous. But man, these characters sure do crack some pretty snappy one-liners. Puss In Boots was ok, Tappy Toes has a couple funny moments, but the Frog Prince is not so good. But that's ok! You have Chop Kick Panda to make it all better!
Any movie that has music and dancing is what my Great Granddaughter loves so she loved this!
